      <title>穆迪称美国债务动态“与 Aaa 评级不一致”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/us-debt-dynamics-inconsistent-with-a-triple-a-rating-moody-s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级在周二发布的一份报告中警告称，下一届美国政府“必须应对不断扩大的预算赤字”，而近一年前，该公司宣布对美国主权信用状况给出负面展望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/us-debt-dynamics-inconsistent-with-a-triple-a-rating-moody-s</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 11:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典央行将无视美联储的领导，暂时保持“渐进式”政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/sweden-s-riksbank-set-to-cut-interest-rates-by-quarter-point-decision-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典央行本周可能会维持其稳定的宽松步伐，而不会像美联储刚刚做出的那样将借贷成本大幅下调半个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/sweden-s-riksbank-set-to-cut-interest-rates-by-quarter-point-decision-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Northvolt 聘请咨询公司 Teneo 解决现金短缺问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/northvolt-hires-advisory-firm-teneo-to-tackle-cash-crunch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，瑞典 Northvolt AB 已聘请咨询公司 Teneo 提供重组建议，包括如果这家债务支持电池制造商未能与贷方达成修改条款时的应急计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/northvolt-hires-advisory-firm-teneo-to-tackle-cash-crunch</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 10:36:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对 Calvin Klein 母公司涉嫌抵制新疆展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-probes-calvin-klein-parent-over-suspected-xinjiang-boycott</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，将对美国服装制造商 PVH 公司因涉嫌抵制来自新疆地区的棉花进行调查，此项调查可能会导致 Tommy Hilfiger 和 Calvin Klein 的母公司受到处罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-probes-calvin-klein-parent-over-suspected-xinjiang-boycott</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 09:40:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
